{"tid":2336214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得Itzy Yeji先係主唱","createTime":"2020-12-22T12:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T16:59:57.000Z","uid":274500,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0adcc4a117a19757b43fb582e02830d5a54aba","tid":2336214,"uid":274500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"Lia每次半開咪都唔夠氣 相反同樣負責chorus嘅yeji好穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之所以推lia主唱係因為要顧及人設 每人都要有專長先唔會比人覺得多餘/人氣唔平均<br />\nyeji本身已經主舞 如果再主唱 而lia得領唱呢個位會好柒<br />\nlia唔識rap又跳舞入面最差所以只能夠推上主唱 咁每個人都有position<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nyeji/彩領-主舞<br />\n留真-rap/center<br />\nyuna- 門面/忙內<br />\nlia-主唱<br />\n<br />\n甚至除咗lia全部都又跳得又穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （但當然chorus難度比較高嘅）<br />\n不過lia都係靚女黎嘅 而且somi走左去solo 更加需要lia因為得佢英文fluent<br />\n跳舞就算 但既然作為主唱佢唱功真係要加強吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申利幾鍾意itzy 希望繼續紅落去"},{"pid":"963e71a45d8191cc907a5fcf8fbb86d6fe716050","tid":2336214,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"幾有心機.."},{"pid":"e9fc58bd41684109104872db271260405faa105d","tid":2336214,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"係掛"},{"pid":"f7e92c1576d134ff5e07dda772951df9e983d65c","tid":2336214,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"f52b1554af4845f38f62ed3d2a5b46aed6053751","tid":2336214,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 馬蹄yeji<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b114fe402d9af3b5150cee76280406f21b67a4b","tid":2336214,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike"